name: designated-critical-habitat
notes: Critical habitats include those areas documented as currently supporting self-sustaining populations of any threatened or endangered species of wildlife as well as those areas determined by the Kansas Department of Wildlife and Parks to be essential for the conservation of any threatened or endangered species of wildlife.
